Package: opentee-engine
Section: devel
Multi-Arch: same
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libtee (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Main Open-TEE framework
 The core of the Open-TEE GlobalPlatform compliant vertual TEE.
 .
 This is required to run any Client or Trusted Applications

