Package: libtee-pkcs11
Section: devel
Multi-Arch: same
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libtee (= ${binary:Version})
Description: PKCS#11 implementation using GP API
 This library provides a PKCS#11 API using a GP compliant TEE as the backend.

Package: libtee-pkcs11-dbg
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libtee-pkcs11 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for PKCS#11 implementation using GP API
 This library provides a PKCS#11 API using a GP compliant TEE as the backend.

Package: libtee-pkcs11-dev
Section: libdevel
Multi-Arch: same
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libtee-pkcs11 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development headers of shared libraries in libtee-pkcs11
 This library allows development of applications that rely on PKCS#11.
